title: Faith in Princes
description: Will and Dan ponder what this podcast is about, continue their discussion of good faith in judging, try to game out exactly what the Court is up to in Dobbs v. Jackson Women's Health, and respond to listener feedback.
author: pod@dividedargument.com (Will Baude & Dan Epps)
